metadata.name: Ra-Avril S2 Fan Art
metadata.description:
Fan art for Avril15- S2 revolving around the topics of Nature, Exploration and Technology. I included things I love as pins on her clothing:

- Acid pin: I'm from the 80's & we all had one back then!  
- 90's R&B: My music vibe  
- Studio Ghibli: best animation films! I love their work.  
- Matrix pills: super mega fan of this film!  
- Avril15 of course  
- NFT forever! 

Digital illustration © Raquel Casilda
